yingyinNormal.en: Why don't we put the repair shed there?
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么不把修车棚建在那儿？

yingyinNormal.en: So I went into the tool shed and I took out an ax.
yingyinNormal.zh: 于是我去工具棚拿来把斧子。

yingyinNormal.en: Have you got a bouncy castle? Yep. A garden shed? Yep. I've got everything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请问一下你有充气城堡吗？有。有花园棚吗？有，我有所有东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Have you got a bouncy castle? Yep. A garden shed? Yep. I've got everything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请问一下你有充气城堡吗？有。有园艺工具棚吗？有，我有所有东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Room's a shed. A shed, Jack? A shed? Okay, good boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 房间是一个棚屋。棚屋，杰克，是棚屋吗？好孩子。

yingyinNormal.en: He put me in his garden shed. Here. Room is the shed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他把我关到他花园的棚屋里，就是这里，房间就是个棚屋。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, south on Elm, three stop signs past the junction with Beech. Look for a garden shed with a skylight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 榆树路南段，距离山毛榉路交叉口有三个停车标志，找一间带天窗的棚屋。

yingyinNormal.en: Can you mend it please, Grandpa Pig? Let's take it to my shed. This is Grandpa Pig's shed, where Grandpa mends things.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你能不能把它修好呢，爷爷？嗯，把这个钟拿到我的小屋里去吧。这里是猪爷爷的小屋，猪爷爷就在这里修理东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Can you mend it please, Grandpa Pig? Let's take it to my shed. This is Grandpa Pig's shed, where Grandpa mends things.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你能不能把它修好呢，爷爷？嗯，把这个钟拿到我的小屋里去吧。这里是猪爷爷的小屋，猪爷爷就在这里修理东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Every couple of days, I have to shed my skin, become someone new.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每隔几天，就得换一层皮，扮个新角色。

yingyinNormal.en: This is Grandpa Pig's shed where he makes things. What have we got here?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是猪爷爷制造东西的小屋。我们这里有什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Grandpa Pig has taken it to his shed. There. That should do it. I am mended.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爷爷把电脑拿去小屋了。好了，这样就可以了。故障解除。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, Grandpa pig has taken it to his shed. There. That should do it. I am mended. Hooray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，猪爷爷把电脑拿去小屋了。好了，这样就可以了。故障解除。太棒了。

yingyinNormal.en: Come on, everyone. Bye bye, Little birds. We're going to make a scarecrow. This is Grandpa pig's garden shed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家跟我来。再见了，小鸟们。我们要去做稻草人了。这是猪爷爷的花园小屋。

yingyinNormal.en: But not too sweet. There's also a salty, gamy thing going on. Yes, that's me. Come on, let's get you outta that shed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但也不是太甜，还有一股酸酸的异味。是我身上的，我放你出来。

yingyinNormal.en: I remember one summer when he was 13, he built a small nuclear reactor in the shed and told everybody he was gonna provide free electricity for the whole town.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我记得他13岁时的夏天他在小屋里做了一个小型原子反应堆，然后跟大家说他会为全镇人提供免费电力。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, no, no. But, I guess everyone deserves a second chance and you're just a lonely old bird and you do have weird manners because you live in a weird shed on the roof.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，但我觉得大家都能有第二次机会。你只是一只孤独的态度很奇怪的老鸟，因为你住在屋顶的怪屋子里。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, when he went on the Internets to get some, a man from the government came by and sat him down real gentle, and told him it's against the law to have yellow-cake uranium in a shed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当他试图上网采购时，一个政府官员来访，很温柔地让他坐下，告诉他私人持有铀精矿是违法的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: to get rid of something that is no longer wanted

examination_example.sentence: In the 10 years ending in 2009, U.S. factories <highlight>shed</highlight> workers so fast that they erased almost all the gains of the previous 70 years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 截至2009年的十年中，美国工厂裁员如此之快，以至于几乎抵消了之前70年所增加的工作机会。

examination_example.sentence: A recent annual study of countries and their ability to convert growth into well-being <highlight>sheds</highlight> some light on that question.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近一项对各国及其将增长转化为福祉的能力进行的年度研究，让人们对这一问题有进一步的了解。

word_usage.usage:
shed light on sth.意为“阐明……；使人了解……”，如：
This book sheds new light on the role of the CIA.
这本书使人们对中央情报局扮演的角色有了进一步的了解。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

examination_example.sentence: The scientists hope their discoveries will <highlight>shed</highlight> light on possible life in outer space.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科学家们希望他们的发现将会揭示外太空可能存在的生命。

examination_example.sentence: A nice video published online last month <highlight>sheds</highlight> light on expertise and the conscious mind.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 上个月网上发布的一段不错的视频阐明了专业知识和意识头脑（之间的关系）。

examination_example.sentence: It <highlight>sheds</highlight> new light on how unhealthy behaviors trigger mental health problems.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它重新揭示了不健康行为是如何引发心理健康问题的。
